data.description: NEW roof, NEW sewer liner, NEW electrical panel! WOW! Situated on a generous lot with incredible outdoor entertaining space, this 3 bed, 2.5 bath property boasts a new white granite kitchen by Tom French Remodeling (2022) and an open floor plan. A fresh neutral paint palette and new thermal windows (2020) adorn the home in bright natural light. Bonus sunroom on main level walks out to the huge back yard featuring three outdoor deck seating areas. Kitchen features new soft close cabinets, large granite island and a separate coffee nook with high quality pull out drawers. You'll be amazed by the double closets and charming trim work in the primary bedroom. Full, dry basement for extra storage. SS appliances stay. Mid-century vibed fireplace on main level. Hardwood floors throughout both levels. Expanded driveway and spacious single car garage. Don't miss this opportunity to live in the heart of KC! Walkable to all things Brookside, Waldo and Crestwood local neighborhoods! Assumable loan opportunity at 4.75% interest rate!
